Package: NetSmartR
Type: Package
Title: Reprioritization of ITN Distribution for Nigerian States
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Grace Legris
Maintainer: Grace Legris <gracebea@gmail.com>
Description: This R package streamlines the analysis and mapping of ward-level reprioritization scenarios for bed net distribution across Nigerian states. It includes tools for:
    - Processing shapefiles
    - Extracting and visualizing environmental and demographic data
    - Classifying settlements
    - Analyzing malaria prevalence
    - Generating reprioritization maps
    Designed to support the National Malaria Elimination Programme (NMEP), the package enables flexible, 
    data-driven decision-making for optimizing malaria intervention strategies.
